INSTALLATION

Standard installation using C++ compiler (better integration
with C++ programs such as ROOT or GEANA) and building the libraries
within the same folder (compatible with tools/bash/load.sh) by
executing the following commands in the adl4 directory:

  ./configure CC=c++ --prefix=$PWD
  make
  make install

-------------------------------------------------------------------

ENVIROMENTAL VARIABLES (NECESSARY FOR EXAMPLES)

To load the necessary enviromental variable in a new shell:

  tools/bash/load.sh

To load the necessary enviromental variables in the current shell:

  source tools/bash/load.sh

------------------------------------------------------------------
